4.00	Tim_McCord	Tim McCord	Timothy McCord (born June 28, 1979 in Sacramento, California) was announced as Evanescence's bass player in August 2006. He replaced bassist Will Boyd who left the band in mid-2006. Previously, McCord was best known for playing guitar for the band The Revolution Smile from 2000 to 2004.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Tim_McCord_of_Evanescence_%40_Maquin%C3%A1ria_Festival.jpg/220px-Tim_McCord_of_Evanescence_%40_Maquin%C3%A1ria_Festival.jpg
